@startuml
title sd ControllaDispositivo

hide footbox
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true

actor Utente
participant SmartHomeSystem as CtrlSystem
participant Room
participant Device as CtrlDevice
participant EventLog as CtrlLog

Utente -> CtrlSystem : controlDevice(device, comando)
activate CtrlSystem
CtrlSystem -> Room : getDevices()
Room --> CtrlSystem : lista dispositivi

alt comando accensione
  CtrlSystem -> CtrlDevice : turnOn()
else comando spegnimento
  CtrlSystem -> CtrlDevice : turnOff()
else comando aggiornamento valore
  CtrlSystem -> CtrlDevice : setValue(value)
end

CtrlDevice --> CtrlSystem : stato o valore aggiornato
CtrlSystem -> CtrlLog : addEvent(DEVICE_UPDATED)
CtrlSystem --> Utente : operazione completata
deactivate CtrlSystem

@enduml
